      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive 996.2 wide-body in collector-grade condition. This example is powered by the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, featuring a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a sophisticated viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system for optimal lateral acceleration. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, equipped with cross-drilled rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers for superior thermal management under braking. Flawless Arctic Silver paint over a supple leather interior, this vehicle shows zero signs of bore scoring and comes with a clean DME over-rev report. A mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the Porsche purist.",
